# Steam Deck Desktop Mode ‚Äì Admin Workstation SOP

This repository contains the Standard Operating Procedure (SOP) for configuring a Steam Deck in Desktop Mode as an administrative workstation. It is designed for sysadmins, developers, and power users who need reliable access to:

- Proxmox and other hypervisors  
- Linux and Windows servers (SSH/RDP)  
- GitHub workflows  
- Website maintenance  
- General administrative tasks  

All documentation is stored in the `docs/` directory.

## üìò Contents

- `docs/SOP_SteamDeck_Admin.md` ‚Äî Full SOP  
- `docs/CHANGELOG.md` ‚Äî Revision history  
- `scripts/setup-checklist.md` ‚Äî Quick setup checklist  

## üõ†Ô∏è Purpose

This SOP defines the standardized procedure for configuring a Steam Deck in Desktop Mode as an administrative workstation for tasks such as server management, RDP/SSH access, GitHub workflows, and website maintenance.

